reviewText: The movie was a steal, so who can argue with that. It also came surprisingly fast, I was really shocked by the fast delivery. It was also in great shape, I'm very happy with it.

I was pleased that my purchase arrived on time and in good condition. The only qualm I had was that I wasn't told the video dragged regularly, no matter how I adjusted the tracking on my vcr. I attributed this to the video's age. It is a classic and is, after all, out of print.

Wee Wendy was one of my favorite VHS movies when I was a child.  If any of you have a little girl, this is a MUST have!!!  I have always adored this movie!  My tape is almost worn out from watching it so much as a child.  I decided to look on Amazon to see by chance if this cartoon was still out there.  I was very pleased to see it was and will be purchasing it soon!
